    <!-- Fix: Blazor enhanced navigation sets tabindex="-1" on <h1> for
         accessibility focus after page transitions. Library CSS loaded above
         (FluentUI reboot.css, DevExpress bootstrap-external, Radzen) adds
         focus outlines/borders. This <style> block loads LAST to override them. -->
